    <values>
        <field>Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Event Monitoring is not capturing ApiTotalUsage or RestApi event types. Programmatic API access that could extract or modify millions of records is not being logged.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Impact__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Programmatic API access can extract or modify millions of records. Without API usage logging, integration misuse, credential theft driving automated access, or rogue integrations are invisible.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Enable ApiTotalUsage and RestApi event types in Setup &gt; Event Manager. Monitor for usage spikes or off-hours API calls via Transaction Security policies or a connected SIEM.</value>
    </values>
